76
00:07:46,660 --> 00:07:48,190
You're so ignorant.

77
00:07:48,190 --> 00:07:51,770
Not knowing what it is, is art. Get it?

78
00:07:51,770 --> 00:07:54,070
Ah, is that so?

79
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:58,800
She was definitely different because she is from the Cheongsong bloodline.

80
00:07:58,830 --> 00:08:00,880
