104
00:09:27,900 --> 00:09:29,410
Your shoes,

105
00:09:29,410 --> 00:09:33,940
the way you count everything in bowls of gamjatang, and earlier at the party too.

106
00:09:33,940 --> 00:09:37,900
Anyway, you're the most fun person I've met.

107
00:09:44,850 --> 00:09:48,860
But you said they already broke up. Why would it be easy to get the 2 billion won?

108
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:52,890
The guy still has feelings for her and is hung up on her.

109
00:09:52,890 --> 00:09:57,140
I heard that even for this funeral, he took care of everything so the bereaved family wouldn't have to worry.

110
00:09:57,140 --> 00:10:00,700
And the woman he loves was confronted with these ignorant...

111
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:05,030
She is in such a bad situation,

112
