174
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:39,270
When does it take place?

175
00:15:39,270 --> 00:15:42,710
It is planned for the first week of October next year.

176
00:15:45,860 --> 00:15:49,130
You must have been really shocked earlier.

177
00:15:52,170 --> 00:15:57,100
How could there be such ignorant people? It's only been a few days since the funeral.

178
00:15:57,100 --> 00:16:00,940
And in front of these sacred art pieces!

179
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:05,130
I've only heard of those thugs and gangsters. It's my first time in twenty years as a curator

180
00:16:05,130 --> 00:16:08,530
