181
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:11,300
I'm sorry.

182
00:16:12,210 --> 00:16:14,040
What?

183
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:19,830
Those ignorant and rude men should be apologizing. Why are you sorry, Director Kim?

184
00:16:22,510 --> 00:16:26,270
Now, you are the director.

185
00:16:27,240 --> 00:16:32,290
To be honest, I thought you were going to close down the art museum.

186
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:35,430
Appearances can be deceiving. Even though it looked like things were fine to others,

187
00:16:35,430 --> 00:16:38,200
you probably know well from watching your father.

188
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:41,220
The reality of art museums in Korea.

189
00:16:42,530 --> 00:16:46,260
Thank you for not giving up

190
00:16:46,260 --> 00:16:48,550
and taking responsibility.

191
00:16:48,550 --> 00:16:51,300
