199
00:17:20,710 --> 00:17:23,640
Fortunately, I'm a fast learner.

200
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:25,790
I believe it.

201
00:17:25,790 --> 00:17:31,640
This is a catalog of the works that have been exhibited so far.

202
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:33,710
Oh, right.

